      <description>
        <![CDATA[
          <h3>Version 1.2.0</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Fixed code signing certificate selection - now correctly uses certificate ID instead of name</li>
            <li>Improved DMG mounting to handle volumes with spaces in names</li>
            <li>Fixed SwiftUI main thread warnings for smoother UI updates</li>
            <li>Enhanced notification system with floating toast notifications at bottom</li>
            <li>Added automatic update checking on app launch</li>
            <li>Added visual update indicator when updates are available</li>
            <li>Fixed all blocking operations to prevent UI freezing</li>
            <li>Improved async handling for file operations and process execution</li>
          </ul>
        ]]>
      </description>
